descript.abstract: This data displays the district boundaries of Indonesia for use in the Interactive Forestry Atlas of Indonesia (2009). It was produced by Badan Pusat Statistik (BPS) from the village data also produced by BPS in 2003. Population data for the year 2000 is also included.
